sources.title: Variety – Varieté (restored) (1925, German Expressionism, imdb score: 7.4)
sources.description: Variety (German: Varieté [ˌvaʀi̯eˈte], also known by the alternative titles Jealousy or Vaudeville) is a 1925 silent drama film directed by Ewald Andre Dupont based on the 1912 novel The Oath of Stephan Huller by Felix Hollaender.
